CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE
This is to certify that West Medway II, LLC assents to and concurs in the rate schedule described below which Exelon West Medway, LLC, has filed, and hereby files this certificate of concurrence in lieu of the filing of the rate schedule specified.
Joint Rate Schedule: Shared Interconnection Facilities Agreement between Exelon West Medway, LLC and West Medway II, LLC
Designated Filing Company (DFC): Exelon West Medway, LLC
DFC Tariff Program: Electric MBR
DFC Tariff Record Adopted by Reference: Exelon West Medway, LLC Rate Schedule No. 1, Shared Interconnection Facilities Agreement, 0.0.0
Dated: June 28, 2016
West Medway II, LLC
/s/ Vincenzo Franco Vincenzo Franco Associate General Counsel Exelon Corporation
